name: Babushka Rattle Doll by LITTLE WISE OWL
description:
These sweet little babushkas are made from vintage and upcycled fabrics, and their internal jingley rattle will amuse your little ones for hours, or if you prefer, they will happily sit quietly on the shelf and charm your friends.  
They measure 21cm, and are stuffed with new polyfill.

name: Bee Off Organic Mosquito Repellent by HONEYCOMB VALLEY
description:
Organic moisturising oils combine with seven essential oils in beeswax to make this organic mosquito repellent that is great for your skin.

When it comes to skincare, the family that live at Honeycomb Valley abide by the principal “you shouldn’t put anything on your skin that isn’t edible."  So honey and beeswax from the hives is melted in sun-oven's on-site, and with the combination of only organic oils, is made into this great purse-sized mosquito repellent that is good enough to eat! (Although we wouldn't recommend it).

It's not bad on the nose, either, in terms of scent, that is!  Combining lemongrass, tea tree and eucalyptus, you'll not smell like a walking chemical bomb, and your kids won't be enhaling all sorts of noxious fumes like some other repellent sprays that shall remain nameless.

Honeycomb Valley chooses to use organic ingredients to blend with farm produce to encourage sustainable farming practices, and to minimise the synthetic chemicals going into the environment.

Ingredients: Organic oils of castor, jojoba, soya bean. Beeswax & honey, organic cocoa butter, carnauba wax.  Organic essential oils of citronella, lavender, geranium, rosemary, eucalyptus, tea tree, lemon eucalyptus, lemongrass.

Be sure to test for allergies before full application.  17gms.

name: Purple Diamond Hairbows by MABEL & DAISY
description: Entirely hand-sewn from vintage and repurposed fabrics, mabel & daisy hairbows are a cute way to add a bit of old-school flair to your hair.  These purple hairbows with a white diamond print are made from a cotton voile and are attached to 45mm gummy alligator clips (no teeth) so they won't snag in your locks.

name: Tree Hello Gift Cards (2 Pack) by LITTLE WISE OWL
description: These sweet little gift cards are made from recycled and upcycled papers on new card stock, and come with cute little envelopes that are just the right size.  Card measures 10cm x 7cm. Pack of two.

name: Organic Cotton Hairbows by MABEL & DAISY
description:
Add a bit of old-school flair to your hair! mabel & daisy are known all over for their hairbows made from vintage and repurposed fabrics but here are the very first from their new organic range.  And these polkadots a cute to boot! You can choose between peach and light blue hairbows made from 100% certified organic cotton. 
They are attached to 45mm gummy alligator clips (no teeth) so they won't snag in your locks, and are a perfect 'in-between' size for both little people and big ones.
